name: Wooden American Made Flag Hand Made Indoor Outdoor Wall Hangings Rustic
description: Wooden American Made Flag Hand Made Indoor Outdoor Wall Hangings Rustic.These hand painted  American Flags are made out of ship lap barn wood. Many layers of paint and polyurethane for long lasting use.Heavy gauge wire for ease of hanging.No two flags are alike.Many different sizes and styles are available on my site at MJOYS on ArtFire. Measures 10 inches x 10 inches to top of wire hanger.Click on picture to enlarge.

name: Paintings Fine Arts Home Decor Troubled Times
description: Paintings Fine Arts Home Decor Troubled Times.This painting is done from imagination alone. A bridge over dark and eerie waters,houses that seem to be groaning and what looks like fire and smoke in the sky.All of these are pointing to trouble.I used a wrapped canvas and acrylic paints,it is sealed.It is suitable for framing but does not come with a frame.Measures 20 inches wide x 16 inches high.This item ships signature confirmation required and is insured. Click on picture to enlarge.

name: Handmade Cloth Doll Art Doll Bohemian Jetta
description: Handmade Cloth Doll Art Doll Bohemian Jetta. This is Jetta,she is a 19 inch Bohemian doll.She was created by me.She has sandels  with pearl straps,lace wrist bands,jeweled arm and wrist bracelets,2 nose earrings,hoop earrings and necklace and jeweled headband. She has a lace scarf to put over her shoulders,which is not shown.She has a few flaws as we all do in the stitching, but are not that noticable. Price reflects the inperfections in her. She does stand but is best leaning against something. She does not come with doll stand.She is not meant to be handled,she is not a toy.Not suitable for children.This Item ships signature confirmation required and is insured.Click on picture to enlarge.

description: Wood Flower Hand Carved Multi Strand Necklace with Large Shell Pendant. Big necklace with hand carved wooden flowers and beads ,bone and pendant.This multi strand necklace is hung on hemp rope and  measures 17 inches long.Click on picture to enlarge.
